    "synopsis": "Word Bearers primarch Lorgar consecrates the largest warship ever built — the Furious Abyss — and slips her into the warp aimed at Macragge, with orders to gut the Ultramarines' homeworld from the void before the Heresy is even declared. A scratch fleet of loyalist Space Marines — Ultramarines under Captain Cestus, a Thousand Sons Librarian, a Space Wolf and a World Eater — hunts her down across the empyrean. A void chase becomes a boarding action becomes a last stand inside the engines of the Abyss herself. The Heresy's most divisive opening chapter: less politics than steel and self-sacrifice.",
